snippet.textDisplay: Ritu raj k ami chintam na, onek din age notun notun ride share app asche oita try kortam, office ses e ekjon k ride share kore basar dike astam. Ekdin lombu jhakra chul wala ekta lok ride share request dilo and ami nilam. Ektu por Najrul songit shuru holo- bhai ami obak hoye shuntesi, rasta haraya feltesi, bhai ke eita, ki gaitese, nojrul songit ki erokom pagol korar moto gan? Nesha dhore gelo. Ekhono oi sriti ta mone ache. Ride share ekhon r korina? Double helmet e rakhina. Ekhon oi apps r ager class nei.
